window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Richard Koch has made a career out of spotting 'Star' businesses - and has made millions from them. </p> <p>Star businesses are ventures operating in a high-growth sector - and are the leaders of their niche in the market. Stars are rare. But with the help of this book and a little patience, you can find one - or create one yourself. </p> <p>This is a vital book for any budding entrepreneur or investor (of grand or modest means). It is also invaluable for any ambitious employee who realises the benefits of working for a Star venture - real responsibility, fast personal development, better pay, great bonuses and valuable share options. </p> <p>Whoever you are, identifying and investing in Stars will make your life much sweeter and richer in every way.</p>"; 
